 FFT to convert it back to the coefficients once again.

28
00:01:34,775 --> 00:01:39,325
 One important point is that FFT converts from the coefficients to the values,

29
00:01:39,325 --> 00:01:42,990
 not for any choice of (X1) through (Xn) but

30
00:01:42,990 --> 00:01:47,130
 for a particular well chosen set of points, (X1) through (Xn).

31
00:01:47,130 --> 00:01:50,310
 And part of the beauty of the FFT algorithm comes from

32
00:01:50,310 --> 00:01:53,775
 this choice of these points (X1) through (Xn).

